<a href="http://www.thepoultrysite.com/poultrynews/23260/crisis-in-ghanas-poultry-industry" target="_self">http://www.thepoultrysite.com/poultrynews/23260/crisis-in-ghanas-poultry...</a></p><p><i>Thebeefsite.com</i>, ‘Ghana’s farming needs investment says official’, 22 July 2011</p><p>
<a href="http://www.thebeefsite.com/news/35328/ghanas-farming-needs-investment-says-official" target="_self">http://www.thebeefsite.com/news/35328/ghanas-farming-needs-investment-sa...</a></p><p>USDA, ‘Brazil Poultry and products Annual 2011’, GAIN report No. BR 0714, 2 September 2011</p><p>
